data.title: IRON FIST S/S'14 LONDON LAUNCH PARTY
data.description:
To launch our Spring/Summer collection landing in the UK, we decided to take over one of Soho's premiere clubs for one night only...
Some of our favorite UK hotties came down to do DJ sets, including While She Sleeps, Alexis Knox, Bury Tomorrow, Rise To Remain & The Skints. 
With a room filled with babes, bands & a HELLA load of booze the outcome was obviously the wildest night London has seen in a long time, and guess what...we caught the whole thing on film.
Keep your eyes peeled for the next IF UK party coming SUMMER 2014. BIGGER, BETTER & BOOZIER.

data.title: IRON FIST CLOTHING || DOWNLOAD 2014 - FRIDAY
data.description:
This year Iron Fist had the honor of being invited down to the mighty Download Festival at Donnington Park, UK and it's safe to say that we were BEYOND stoked!
With a line-up that boasted the likes of Aerosmith, Linkin Park, Killswitch Engage, Trivium, Steel Panther, The Offspring & many, many more, we had a feeling it was going to be a weekend to remember. And with enough beer, bands, babes & of course a bunch of awesome IF swag, what could possibly go wrong?

We caught up with a load of your favorite bands to find out how it felt to be playing the biggest rock & metal festival in the UK, what exactly is so special about Download, their top festival tips, and a bunch of other random sh*t!

Check out the first installment from the Download x IF weekender, featuring the likes of Huntress, Within Temptation, Skindred, The Amity Affliction, Battlecross, Radkey, Orange Goblin & Baby Godzilla. And make sure you stayed tune for much, much more.
